			<p>
				You need to take the following steps:
				<ul>
					<li>You need to register with IRCT web-site and set up an account.</li>
					<li>IRCT staff will get back to you when the information you have provided has been verified and accepted.</li>
				</ul>
			</p>
			<p><a href="/page/how_to_register_a_trial">Read more &raquo;</a></p>
		</div>
		
		
